Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold bells and a bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose they\Nwere symbols of old Jaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno, but I think they were\Npart of some sort of model.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This here's called a South Bird,\Nand they still exist on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Do they have weird calls?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Just like the logbook says!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailors have long used South Birds to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.88,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go catch this bird! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we need a bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely! The Knock-Up Stream\Nyou're heading for tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is located directly south of this cape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're on the open sea,\Nthere's no way to get your bearings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading for ocean, not an island,\Nso we have no guide to rely on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.38,0:02:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll use the bird's behavior for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the sad tale of your\NMontblanc family at the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It moved me, Cricket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure someone else struggled to\Nget has a special flavor all its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna know what people call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hyena!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dreams Don't Come True?!\NBellamy versus the Saruyama Alliance"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come! Dodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These praying mantises aren't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Our net!\N--What's with this forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's him!\N--What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The South Bird is the bugs' control tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:04:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a bird controlling bugs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here! Where's it coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? I hear something different...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Up ahead!\N--Huh? Boulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're rolling this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it dung beetle dung?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! They're bugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladybugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn things!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is your mole cricket army attacking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way! Do you\Nthink you can beat me?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it, but I can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Slug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Salt! Throw salt!\N--Sanji! Your Somersault Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright!\N--Not that kind of "salt"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:05:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of running! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Luffy! Bear-bees are really poisonous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fireflies!\N--So pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cockroaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gladly accept fights people pick with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the Saruyama Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over your gold quietly,\Nor else you're gonna pay dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you figure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it's dangerous for kids\Nto swing stuff like that around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I guess we should\Nget this midnight show started!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:07:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Bellamy! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of our captain's\N"Spring-Spring Fruit" powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speechless, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up the trash! Take care of 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for your Saruyama Alliance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just an old man and\Na couple of overgrown apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jackpot, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Would you look at that?\NWonderful gold bullion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This's a big haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys... aren't qualified to have that gold...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Qualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this qualified enough for ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:08:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're way stronger than you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much more qualified do we\Nneed to be to steal treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, old-timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Havoc Sonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sarquiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that again... The power\Nof the Spring-Spring Fruit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Shojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:09:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer! We found gold! A bell-shaped ingot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It matches what's listed\Nin the logbook! It mentions bells!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go. Load the gold on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grow up, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "city of gold" is just a\Nproduct of Noland's imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna be a pirate\Nin the coming new era,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:10:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you need to realize\Nthat dreams never come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city of gold does exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Don't go wild! It's a small house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, kiddo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hatchling who doesn't have the\Nguts to pick fights with dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is in no position to talk about pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No luck. We couldn't even see a single one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.50,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw one, but there was no time\Nfor the bird, with all those bugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we did was run...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh! Seven people, and you get zilch?!\NGet it together, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You really think you can catch us? Idiots!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He came here to tell us that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'll shoot you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I needed was to see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy! We caught a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old diamond-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masira!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.73,0:12:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Gimme a hand!\N--Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The Going Merry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Who did this?!\NDammit! Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sorry...\N--Old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, old guy! Are you awake?!\N--I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we could do! We're pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... there's still time to\Nstrengthen the ship before sunup...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, old guy! Tell us what happened first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's okay. Don't worry about it.\NDoesn't matter now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Great! You caught yourselves a South Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:13:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gold... It's been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's alright... Forget about that junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to focus on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "junk"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took you ten long years\Nof diving into the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and torturing your body\Nuntil you found that gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can't just...\N--Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright... This's our problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they all work on it, the Saruyama Alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can fix and reinforce that ship, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have 'em finish in time for morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be any trouble\Nwith your departure tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! We will send you\Ninto the sky, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy's mark...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Luffy! Don't be stupid!\NWe set sail in only three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I run along the coast, will I reach\Nthe town from this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid! Where're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool! Do you\Nknow who you're dealing--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna stop him, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back by morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm empty now! That's every\Nlast drop of water in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I won't sweat a single drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:15:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ol' drunk is broke and dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O, God of Alcohol, thank you for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess there's no such thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see! What bad news is there today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this isn't a newspaper.\NIt's a stack of wanted posters...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this is a lawless town!\NI'm sick of meeting new bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is that spineless kid from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that sky island talk was a real hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty million, I believe he was worth...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! I had a little too much to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 10, 100, 1,000, 10,000,\N100,000, 1,000,000, 10,000,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:16:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! I really did drink too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 10, 100, 1,000, 10,000,\N100,000, 1,000,000, 10,000,000...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...100,000,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we delay our departure any more than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll lose your chance to go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've done reckless diving day after day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without letting those bubbles\Ndisappear from his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a duel with the man\Nwho screwed up my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm truly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we could do! We're pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:17:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those big apes were hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had huge gashes all over\Nand had tears and snot dripping down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as they cried, "Old-timer!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's that important,\Nthey should've protected him better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't help it; they were\Nup against you and Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, our captain is a major\Nrookie worth 55 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?! It's the middle of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon! Those guys in here, they--!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Bellamy! You're still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta get out of here!\NYou're in the most danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about? Me, in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,60 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Those two from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bounties are higher than yours, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:19:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're dead meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?! Crap!\NWe laughed at the wrong people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think they remember what we look like?!\NIt's dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never met anyone with a 100 million bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey! You fools!\NScared of a few scraps of paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have knotholes for eyes?!\NYou saw their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that there were once pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who faked their own wanted posters\Nto make names for themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People'd see their bounties\Nand just curl up and surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though they could've won in a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you guys now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw how weak they are,\Nbut look at you now! You're pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Boy, those\Nbastards had me scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy's right-- someone\Nwith a bounty of 100 million
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has gotta be involved\Nwith some pretty bad stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then why hasn't he been in the papers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely! I ain't heard of any straw hat kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! Had me scared for a minute there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Back to drinking! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:21:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he'd call me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard the rumors about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Give back old diamond-head's gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were goin' to\Na sky island. How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to head into the sky...\Nafter I beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.12,0:23:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you ever say is dream-like crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.69,0:23:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I can make you\Ndream forever... in the afterlife!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.63,0:23:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"100 Million Man! World's Greatest\NPower and Pirate Blackbeard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
